  "title": "Operations Manager (5.5 Days) $5K - $5.5K + VB + Transport Provided (West Area) – Waste Treatment Industry",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role Summary</strong> </p><p>Manage hazardous waste treatment production lines with evaporation, centrifugation, and filtration technologies. Ensure safe, compliant operations while supporting sales team with technical capacity planning.</p><p><strong>Key Duties</strong></p><p>·      Operate and optimize waste treatment production lines (evaporation, centrifuge, filtration systems)</p><p>·      Plan production schedules and coordinate resources to meet throughput targets</p><p>·      Oversee equipment maintenance, troubleshooting, and team management</p><p>·      Provide technical support to sales on capacity, feasibility, and processing timelines</p><p>·      Maintain compliance with EHS requirements and regulatory standards</p><p>·      Manage documentation for audits and inspections</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>·      Bachelor's Degree in Chemical / Environmental / Process / Mechanical Engineering or related field</p><p>·      10+ years in Industrial Production (hazardous waste treatment, chemical processing, or environmental industries preferred)</p><p>·      Hands-on experience with evaporation systems, centrifuges, or filtration equipment</p><p>·      Strong production planning, team leadership, and cross-functional communication skills</p><p>📧<strong>Apply Now: </strong><a href=\"mailto:jeffrey@oaktree.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">jeffrey@oaktree.com.sg</a><br />👤<strong>Contact:</strong> Jeffrey Chua Kay Hwee<br />EA License No: 06C4642 | EA Reg No: R1110624</p>",
